{"tid":162544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人識得破自稱抑鬱依招？","createTime":"2017-03-19T11:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T11:47:16.000Z","uid":66436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b97c53c92476700e07b95f371620f1d6af99526e","tid":162544,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"次次見到都唔夠打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147552f7eba4b394a54fc481bba4f129b6d9eb65","tid":162544,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"點樣唔夠打<br />\n<br />\n當年打機識得一個<br />\n<br />\n佢新制dse讀緊中四<br />\n<br />\n然後唔知因為咩原因<br />\n<br />\n可能讀書 可能感情 乜q物q<br />\n<br />\n總之自稱抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n然之後從此唔肯返學<br />\n<br />\n佢仲絕到話就算父母打爆佢電腦<br />\n<br />\n佢都唔會肯去第二間學校面試<br />\n<br />\n我唔知佢係咪真係夠膽死唔考dse<br />\n<br />\n不過似乎真係冇考到<br />\n<br />\n佢話抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n但抑鬱得好開心<br />\n<br />\n周圍去玩 拍拖溝仔 食飯 睇戲 行街<br />\n<br />\n連老母都睇唔過眼話佢 我諗可能因為見佢唔返學但仲有心情去睇戲<br />\n<br />\n屌有話錯佢咩<br />\n<br />\n佢學人玩界手<br />\n<br />\n有d人對自己真係好狼死既 而且唔會俾人發現<br />\n<br />\n但佢只係小學雞用鎖匙界手咁既程度 條痕只係少少紅腫<br />\n<br />\n屌真係好撚肉酸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等佢仲有面擺上fb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aeef985d92d98c2a9e1aa262e863ed3fc1934c","tid":162544,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:13:58.000Z","msg":"抑鬱而家周街都係啦<br />\n<br />\n香港醫院精神科情緒病係遠遠多過重性精神病"},{"pid":"ac56f155f010cdb1c31b60fa2779398815f77bca","tid":162544,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"醫生紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"6a2fda005abd6f052c9fd0d5f238aa01fe10bfdd","tid":162544,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><b